DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 22-2-2-14.1.
Synopsis: Tip pooling. Specifically authorizes the use of tip pooling
arrangements under certain circumstances.
Effective: June 27, 2024 (retroactive).
Freeman, Rogers
January 8, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Pensions and Labor.
